Package org.cyclops.integratedcrafting.core

Class CraftingJobHandler

java.lang.Object
org.cyclops.integratedcrafting.core.CraftingJobHandler
public class CraftingJobHandler extends Object
A CraftingJobHandler maintains a list of processing and pending crafting job. Each time that update(INetwork, int, PartPos) is called, the handler will observe the target position for changes in the processing job. Also, it will try initiating pending jobs into the target if none was running.
